{"id":"omnidist-0g8","title":"Expand test coverage for release pipeline paths","description":"Add table-driven tests for version resolution, npm config validation, stage/verify behaviors, and publish argument construction to prevent release regressions.","notes":"Added unit tests for shim generation, npm distribution validation, version resolution (env/file/errors), and publish argument construction. Remaining: add stage/verify integration-style tests around artifact/version parity flows.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:43:21.505585958+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:50:45.744046103+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:50:45.744046103+06:00","close_reason":"Expanded release-path coverage with tests for config/version resolution, publish args, and stage+verify integration mismatch detection."}
{"id":"omnidist-8k2","title":"Publish npm patch release for platform package resolution","description":"Published @omnidist/omnidist@0.1.1 fails at runtime on global install because shim expects platform package as sibling directory. Need release with require.resolve-based platform package lookup and verify global install on linux/mac/windows.","notes":"Code fix committed in b1ce231: shim now resolves @scope/pkg-\u003cplatform\u003e via require.resolve. Remaining work: stage/publish v0.1.2 and verify npm i -g @omnidist/omnidist works on target platforms.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:22:31.659645201+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:36:07.220836681+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:36:07.220836681+06:00","close_reason":"v0.1.2 tagged, published, and install verified by user."}
{"id":"omnidist-bkf","title":"Propagate chmod errors during npm stage","description":"stagePlatformPackage ignores chmod error on non-Windows binaries. Return failure when chmod fails to avoid shipping non-executable binaries.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:43:01.778304901+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:19.853559195+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:19.853559195+06:00","close_reason":"stagePlatformPackage now propagates chmod failures for non-Windows binaries."}
{"id":"omnidist-edo","title":"Honor npm registry/access config in publish","description":"npm publish currently hardcodes --access public and ignores configured distribution registry unless explicit CLI override is provided. Use config defaults and only override when flags are set.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:43:01.436263456+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:24.883220862+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:24.883220862+06:00","close_reason":"Publish now uses validated npm distribution defaults for access/registry, with CLI override precedence for --registry."}
{"id":"omnidist-ohj","title":"Fix npm shim platform package resolution for global installs","description":"Global installs of @omnidist/omnidist@0.1.1 fail because shim assumes platform package is sibling. Resolve package path with require.resolve and full scoped package name.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:26:53.434686776+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:28:28.151036902+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:28:28.151036902+06:00","close_reason":"Implemented shim fix (require.resolve + scoped package name), added regression test, and adjusted .gitignore path anchoring."}
{"id":"omnidist-ov5","title":"Validate npm distribution config before commands","description":"Stage, verify, and publish assume cfg.Distributions[\"npm\"] exists and is valid. Add central validation and clear user-facing error messages for missing/invalid fields.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:43:01.906185526+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:19.876418308+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:19.876418308+06:00","close_reason":"Added central npm distribution validation (presence, package required, access enum) and wired stage/verify/publish through it."}
{"id":"omnidist-r1h","title":"Remove dead code from config and root command","description":"Delete unused NPMConfig type and unused ExitOnError helper (or start using it consistently) to reduce API surface and maintenance overhead.","status":"closed","priority":3,"issue_type":"chore","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:43:26.585491487+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:50:40.64140372+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:50:40.64140372+06:00","close_reason":"Removed unused NPMConfig type and deleted unused ExitOnError helper in root command."}
{"id":"omnidist-ypr","title":"Fail fast on invalid/unknown release version","description":"Version resolution falls back to 0.0.0 on failures and reads VERSION file without trimming whitespace. Return explicit errors for unresolved version sources and trim file/env values.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","owner":"alexey.samoylov@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-02-19T20:43:06.559546796+06:00","created_by":"Alexey Samoylov","updated_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:19.928522506+06:00","closed_at":"2026-02-19T20:47:19.928522506+06:00","close_reason":"Version resolution now fails fast on unknown/missing sources and trims whitespace from env/file versions."}
